'''Environmental bastion armor''' was an advanced, upgradeable environment suit used around the time of the [[Mandalorian Wars]] and [[Jedi Civil War]]. The suit was designed to offer complete protection from temperature extremes, sonic extremes, and many forms of toxins&mdash;all while offering solid protection from combat. With additional modifications, the armorsuit could be converted into a fully contained [[Environment suit/Legends|enviro-suit]] capable of affording the wearer protection from radiation.<ref name="KOTOR">[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]</ref>

